'''Dormo-shock''' was a natural reaction to a severe physical or emotional trauma that induced a coma-like condition. [[Commander/Legends|Commander]] [[Luke Skywalker/Legends|Luke Skywalker]] once suffered from dormoshock, but responded well to [[Bacta/Legends|bacta]] treatment.

